snippet.description:
In a small village plagued by a rising tide of drug-related deaths, the mysterious overdose of a young man named Babbu sparks a web of suspicion and intrigue.

After the success of "Yaar Jigree Kasooti Degree" and "Yaar Chale Bahar"  Troll Punjabi is back with a Mystery Series "KHADPANCH" - A gripping tale of a Punjab's Village torn apart by addiction, secrets, and the relentless pursuit of justice.


Edited, Produced, Written & Directed - Rabby Tiwana (Insta :-  @rabbytiwana)

Starring - Amrit Amby (IG : @amritamby),  Sukh Pindi Wala AKA Dhutta (IG : @pindi_ala),  Amrita Amme (IG : @Amrita Amme), Butta Badbar (IG : @buttabadbar).

Vocals - Gurpreet Singh, Gron Sukhija
Music - Gurpreet Singh (Hertz Music Studio)
Lyrics - Kunwar Partap

After a shocking theft in the city connects back to the village, tensions rise as Vicky‚Äôs investigation deepens into Babbu‚Äôs mysterious death.

snippet.description:
Experience the magic of love with Tu Hai Toh Main Hoon from Sky Force! This soulful melody, sung by Arijit Singh and Afsana Khan, beautifully captures the essence of love and togetherness. Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

Subhe subhe subhe subhe teri yaadein
Subhe subhe subhe subhe din bana de

Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon
Bas main tera hoon tu hain toh main hoon
Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Ek mutthi khwahishon ki tere aage khol ke
Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke
Na tere saaye pe bhi aaye koi aanch dua maangoon
Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Tu rang mein, teri pehchaan hoon
Pehchaan hoon, main teri jaan hoon
Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode
Yaad kisi ka haath na chhode
Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

Experience the magic of love with Tu Hai Toh Main Hoon from Sky Force! This soulful melody, sung by Arijit Singh and Afsana Khan, beautifully captures the essence of love and togetherness. Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Song Credits:
Song name - Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon
Singer - Arijit Singh , Afsana khan
Music - Tanishk Bagchi 
Lyrics - Irshad kamil
Starcast - Veer Pahariya, Sara Ali Khan
Programming - Tanishk Bagchi
Additional Programming- Krishna Kishore
Drums - Stuart Brown ( Scotland ) 
Guitars - Keba Jeremiah 
Nylon Guitars - Ben (Scotland) 
Rhythm - Krishna Kishor 
Woodwinds - Ashish 
Solo Humming - Kamalaja 
Female - Kamalaja, Sri Radha , Fathima 
Dubbing Engineers - Lijesh & Mani Ratnam
Violin Solo-Jeetendra 
Mix and master - Eric Pillai @ Future Sound Of Bombay
Hookline inspired from Mohsen Yeganeh song ‚ÄúBehet Ghol Midam‚Äù

Movie Credits:
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Produced By: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced By: Amar Kaushik
Producer: Sahil Baber Khan
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Poonam Shivdasani & Komal Kewlani
Written By: Carl Austin (UK), Sandeep Kewlani and Aamil Keeyan Khan
Additional Screenplay & Dialogues By: Niren Bhatt
Director Of Photography: Santhana Krishanan Ravichandran
Director of Choreography- Vijay Ganguly

Lyrics:-

Subhe subhe subhe subhe teri yaadein
Subhe subhe subhe subhe din bana de
Tu meri kheedkiyo pe bikhre din banke
Tu mujhpe dhoop sa hai girta chan chan ke
Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon
Bas main tera hoon tu hain toh main hoon
Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Antara:
Ek mutthi khwahishon ki tere aage khol ke
Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke
Na tere saaye pe bhi aaye koi aanch dua maangoon
Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Tu rang mein, teri pehchaan hoon
Pehchaan hoon, main teri jaan hoon
Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode
Yaad kisi ka haath na chhode
Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

snippet.title: Skoda Kylaq Manual & AT Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Skoda India is finally shipping their cars to dealerships, and you can buy them. It has been a long wait for many prospective buyers, considering we first saw the car last year, and it is ready, but it is now, in January 2025, that buyers will see it. But no matter what, this is an essential car for Skoda India. It did spark interest in customers when the introductory price was accounted. Here is a detailed video of manual and automatic drivetrains I recorded recently in Goa.

05:50 Skoda Kylaq rear seat space and issues
08:10 Boot space
09:33 Skoda Kylaq 1 Liter AT drive Impressions

19:51 Conclusion

snippet.title: Snow Day Vlog in Tamil | Making a Snow Man | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me during our recent experience with snow fall. We had never experienced this heavy snow before and we had a great time playing with snow balls and we also built a snowman. Alandra had a great time playing in the snow. We had already protected the cold sensitive plants in the greenhouse and wrapped others. It was a very good experience having snow as a temporary guest and seeing the whole landscape in a bright white color. 

Friends, hope you like today's vlog. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | PSG 4-2 MAN CITY | Grealish, Haaland Goals | UEFA Champions League
snippet.description:
City will need to beat Club Brugge next week to qualify for the Champions League play-off round after a 4-2 defeat to PSG.
The Blues saw a two -goal lead slip against the impressive French champions who responded with an outstanding fight-back

After a goalless first-half, quickfire second period goals from Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland looked to have set City on the road to a priceless victory.

But two goals in four minutes for PSG wiped out our advantage in the blink of an eye, a third from Joao Neves 12 minutes from time and a Gon√ßalo Ramos fourth with the last kick of the game gave the Ligue 1 champions a dramatic 4-2 win.

snippet.title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
He‚Äôs dying to save mankind. #Mickey17 ‚Äì only in theaters March 7.

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the job‚Ä¶ to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, ‚ÄúMickey 17‚Äù stars Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúTenet‚Äù), Naomi Ackie (‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù), Academy Award nominee Steven Yeun (‚ÄúMinari,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeef‚Äù), with Academy Award nominee Toni Collette (‚ÄúHereditary‚Äù), and Academy Award nominee Mark Ruffalo (‚ÄúPoor Things‚Äù). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner and Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winners for ‚ÄúMoonlight‚Äù and ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù ‚ÄúSnowpiercer‚Äù). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúBardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúThe Favourite,‚Äù ‚ÄúCruella‚Äù). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The music is by Jung Jaeil (‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù ‚ÄúSquid Game‚Äù). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,‚Äù ‚ÄúFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw‚Äù). The costume designer is Catherine George (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù Snowpiercer‚Äù). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents A Plan B Entertainment Production, An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on March 7, 2025, and internationally beginning on 5 March 2025.

Chhaava, starring Vicky Kaushal, Rashmika Mandanna and Akshaye Khanna, directed by Laxman Utekar dropped its trailer on Wednesday. The trailer of the film presents Vicky as the fearless Maratha warrior, Chhatrapati Sambhaji Maharaj, who took the throne after the death of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, the founder of the Maratha empire.
